### Security test - client role and tenantId must be ignored
POST http://localhost:5000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyName": "Security Test",
  "companySlug": "security-test",
  "adminName": "Bad Client",
  "email": "bad-client@test.com",
  "password": "StrongPass123!",
  "role": "SUPER_ADMIN",
  "tenantId": "fake-tenant-id"
}
